{"tid":520482,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"防雷拖板選擇","createTime":"2018-01-05T12:59:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-05T23:02:12.000Z","uid":122197,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d7e311394a9d8347b2d3f9c04283fc8bc564730a","tid":520482,"uid":122197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T12:59:34.000Z","msg":"岩岩出左旺角同鴨記，睇緊幾隻牌子既防雷拖板<br />\n<br />\nbrennenstuhl<br />\nschneider<br />\nbelkin<br />\n<br />\n想知邊隻牌子信得過? brennenstuhl網上有人話幾好，但我去到鋪頭，個拖板係用好cheap既膠包住，包裝紙上面仲有唔知泰文定印尼文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔肯定係咪假貨/水貨<br />\n<br />\nschneidar屋企有用開，都ok，不過佢隻防雷拖板連埋usb叉電位，我唔想要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  聽過人講有usb位既拖板無咁㩒用<br />\n<br />\nbelkin自己未用開，剩係知佢本身做開router/手機叉電器，唔肯定佢做拖板做得好唔好"},{"pid":"11e145b46052662117e74e24865fd54d9ad1bc77","tid":520482,"uid":57214,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T13:05:20.000Z","msg":"你自己都揀咗囉<br />\n就係belkin囉仲要開post問<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"909ae9c1567cf171062cfaac8212c3200060b6ab","tid":520482,"uid":32549,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T13:06:33.000Z","msg":"belkin 囉<br />\n其他乜9 黎"},{"pid":"4161bcbbff7ef1d785bbd14b8adeb960b4dd15be","tid":520482,"uid":122197,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"11e145b46052662117e74e24865fd54d9ad1bc77","tid":520482,"uid":57214,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T13:05:20.000Z","msg":"你自己都揀咗囉<br />\n就係belkin囉仲要開post問<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T13:31:01.000Z","msg":"就係揀唔落手先開post問囉，你見我三隻牌子都各有好同唔好"},{"pid":"9f66ce0a33486557816404946c527556f438175b","tid":520482,"uid":25003,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T13:36:27.000Z","msg":"五金店買咪算<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba08776ac1a710b6d8c3a47c8192518f03f5a2ed","